Title: Application Container Boot - Init
participant AppCon participant AppMon participant Child Process
AppCon-->AppCon: Load list of applications
Note left of AppCon: For each application Note left of AppCon: Case 1:\n app folder is missing AppCon-->AppMon: sendcmd("remove") AppMon-->Child Process: "stop/die" signal AppCon-->AppCon: remove app from list Note left of AppCon: End Case 1 Note left of AppCon: Case 2:\n app is runnable AppCon-->AppMon: sendcmd("setup") Note left of AppCon: Case 2.1:\n autostart is true AppCon-->AppMon: sendcmd("start") AppMon-->Child Process: fork() Note right of Child Process: execute \n application Child Process-->AppMon: "ok" AppMon-->AppCon: "ok" Note left of AppCon: End Case 2.1 Note left of AppCon: End Case 2 Note left of AppCon: End loop
AppCon->AppCon: Save application list
